{"about_the_game":"Storybook of Tactics mixes deck building gameplay with a colorful auto battler. As a commander, you can feel the tactical depth with equipping items, obtaining powers, and placing units of your evolving army to crush multiple waves of enemies and powerful bosses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Endless replayability</h2>Randomly generated maps across multiple locations, a selection of leaders with unique powers, and risk-and-reward in-game events ensure that surprise awaits at every corner.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/new_gif_mapa.gif?t=1730752911\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tactical yet accessible auto battler</h2>New players to the genre can quickly understand the rules of making a successful army, and loosing a battle doesn't require a frustrating restart. Auto battler veterans can fight for flawless victories with more difficult map modifiers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/gif_units_final.gif?t=1730752911\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Flexible playstyles</h2>You are free to experiment with the available tactics and choose the right one for your style of play, the rules of the map and the type of enemies. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/new_gif_karty.gif?t=1730752911\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Colorful 2D art</h2>From animations &amp; UI, diverse locations, appealing visuals of bosses, to design of enemies and skills - everything is colorful and pleasant. But don't let your guard down! <br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2511340/extras/new_encounter.gif?t=1730752911\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Protagonist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2511340/59fed44761078bcc2e81e7956935223c